				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The DPCM channel is just not good at high-frequency content. It can only do it quietly, if at all.<br /><br />For this specific case, you might find <a href="https://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=5334" class="postlink">my tool</a> to convert samples to a noise channel sequence useful.</div>

