						<div class="postbody">Another thing to watch out for is where the delta counter is during your sample's playback.  If your sample isn't loud enough to reset the &quot;midpoint&quot; of the sample, this can be a thing (and even if it IS loud enough, you can tilt the data toward zero with RJDMC and FamiTracker).</div>

					
